130
00:09:27,668 --> 00:09:29,970
<i>It's so hard</i>
<i>to keep these festivals alive,</i>

131
00:09:30,104 --> 00:09:31,972
<i>so your response</i>
<i>has lifted our spirits.</i>

132
00:09:32,106 --> 00:09:33,540
