133
00:09:33,674 --> 00:09:35,776
When was the last time
you went to Starbucks?

134
00:09:35,909 --> 00:09:39,113
<i>On behalf of lovers</i>
<i>of literature</i>
<i>everywhere, I thank you.</i>

135
00:09:39,246 --> 00:09:41,448
<i>And I hope</i>
<i>this is not too forward of me,</i>

136
00:09:41,582 --> 00:09:43,350
<i>but it would be wonderful</i>
<i>if you could perhaps</i>

137
00:09:43,484 --> 00:09:45,619
<i>share a piece</i>
<i>of new writing with us.</i>

138
00:09:45,753 --> 00:09:48,055
<i>- I don't write.
- </i> <i>Most writers</i> <i>don't write.</i>

139
00:09:48,188 --> 00:09:50,157
