about not writing,

140
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:52,259
then they write about
not writing.

141
00:09:53,394 --> 00:09:56,230
<i>And they're depressed.</i>
<i>You're always depressed.</i>

142
00:10:23,157 --> 00:10:26,627
<i>Looks like we're having</i>
<i>a crisis of inspiration.</i>

143
00:10:27,561 --> 00:10:28,595
Mmm.

144
00:10:30,798 --> 00:10:33,934
<i>Oh, I know,</i>
<i>it's that you're a drunk</i>

145
00:10:34,836 --> 00:10:36,437
<i>and an impostor.</i>

146
00:10:40,875 --> 00:10:43,944
You just happen to
share a name
with the writer.

147
00:10:45,012 --> 00:10:46,547
The arrogance.

148
00:10:47,514 --> 00:10:49,583
They asked me
to write something.

149
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:51,118
It's ridiculous.

150
00:10:51,251 --> 00:10:53,120
Put down the pencil,

151
00:10:54,488 --> 00:10:55,589
