<i>The watermark</i>
<i>appeared on my ceiling</i>

153
00:11:22,382 --> 00:11:25,552
<i>on the rainy day</i>
<i>my wife walked out on me.</i>

154
00:11:32,459 --> 00:11:34,561
<i>At first it was just a spot,</i>

155
00:11:34,695 --> 00:11:37,030
<i>approximately the size</i>
<i>of a quarter,</i>

156
00:11:37,164 --> 00:11:40,234
<i>directly above the bed</i>
<i>where I lay weeping.</i>

157
00:11:40,367 --> 00:11:42,269
<i>Listening to the rain fall,</i>

158
00:11:42,402 --> 00:11:43,905
<i>I watched the watermark grow</i>

159
00:11:44,037 --> 00:11:47,007
<i>ever so slowly</i>
<i>to the size of...</i>

160
